'''史考特·M·詹森'''（{{lang-en|Scott M. Jensen}}，{{bd|1954年|11月19日|}}）是[[美國|美國]]政治人物、[[醫師|醫師]]，[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]籍，曾任[[明尼蘇達州參議院|明尼蘇達州參議院]]議員。

== 生平 ==
曾就讀[[路德神學院|路德神學院]]和[[明尼蘇達大學|明尼蘇達大學]]，1981年在明尼蘇達大學獲得[[醫學博士|醫學博士]]學位<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Jensen, Scott|url=https://www.lrl.mn.gov/legdb/fulldetail?ID=15484|accessdate=2021-01-23|publisher=Minnesota Legislature|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204181147/https://www.lrl.mn.gov/legdb/fulldetail?ID=15484|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

詹森在{{le|沃特敦 (明尼蘇達州)|Watertown, Minnesota|沃特敦}}成立了Catalyst診所。他還曾擔任{{le|明尼蘇達大學醫學院|University of Minnesota Medical School}}家庭實踐系的臨床副教授<ref>{{Cite web|title=Candidates file for state seats: DFL pits veterans against incumbent Republican rep, doctor|url=https://www.hometownsource.com/sun_patriot/news/local/candidates-file-for-state-seats-dfl-pits-veterans-against-incumbent-republican-rep-doctor/article_ca6ffe37-771e-507a-9357-80fa91b20327.html|accessdate=2021-01-23|date=2016-06-30|publisher=Sun Patriot|language=en}}</ref>。

2016年當選明尼蘇達州參議院議員。2019年7月，詹森宣布他不會在2020年競選連任<ref>{{Cite web|title=State Sen. Scott Jensen is not running again — and he has a lot to say about the Legislature: ‘This is a really bizarre place’|url=https://www.minnpost.com/state-government/2019/07/state-sen-scott-jensen-is-not-running-again-and-he-has-a-lot-to-say-about-the-legislature-this-is-a-really-bizarre-place/|accessdate=2021-01-23|date=2019-07-26|work=MinnPost|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204042313/https://www.minnpost.com/state-government/2019/07/state-sen-scott-jensen-is-not-running-again-and-he-has-a-lot-to-say-about-the-legislature-this-is-a-really-bizarre-place/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年2月，詹森提出了一項法案，以成立一個新的委員會調查藥品價格的上漲<ref>{{Cite web|title=Top idea for lowering drug prices may be too controversial to become law|url=https://www.twincities.com/2020/02/19/top-idea-for-lowering-drug-prices-may-be-too-controversial-to-become-law/|accessdate=2021-01-23|date=2020-02-19|work=Twin Cities|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203043404/https://www.twincities.com/2020/02/19/top-idea-for-lowering-drug-prices-may-be-too-controversial-to-become-law/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年4月，詹森質疑[[2019冠狀病毒病美國疫情|新冠肺炎]][[2019冠状病毒病死亡病例数|死亡人數]]的真實性，批評[[美国疾病控制与预防中心|美国疾病控制与预防中心]]的紀錄方式可能誇大了新冠肺炎的死亡人數<ref>{{Cite web|title=Minnesota doctor blasts 'ridiculous' CDC coronavirus death count guidelines|url=https://www.foxnews.com/media/physician-blasts-cdc-coronavirus-death-count-guidelines|accessdate=2021-01-23|date=2020-04-09|last=Creitz|first=Charles|work=Fox News|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210222141122/https://www.foxnews.com/media/physician-blasts-cdc-coronavirus-death-count-guidelines|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Minnesota doctor questions coronavirus death toll, claims 'influenza deaths ... have been called COVID-19'|url=https://www.foxnews.com/media/dr-scott-jensen-cdc-coronavirus-death-guidelines|accessdate=2021-01-23|date=2020-04-28|last=Halon|first=Yael|work=Fox News|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111072033/https://www.foxnews.com/media/dr-scott-jensen-cdc-coronavirus-death-guidelines|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年7月初，詹森表示，因為有人針對他之前的言論向明尼蘇達州醫療實踐委員會投訴，他目前正在接受明尼蘇達州醫療實踐委員會的調查<ref>{{Cite web|title=Local state senator, physician under investigation by state board|url=https://www.hometownsource.com/sun_patriot/local-state-senator-physician-under-investigation-by-state-board/article_b3a06ea0-c077-11ea-9ae5-eb7b674660ae.html|accessdate=2021-01-23|date=2020-07-07|publisher=Sun Patriot|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200709082820/https://www.hometownsource.com/sun_patriot/local-state-senator-physician-under-investigation-by-state-board/article_b3a06ea0-c077-11ea-9ae5-eb7b674660ae.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。明尼蘇達州參議院多數黨領袖{{le|保羅·賈齊卡|Paul Gazelka}}支持詹森，並說詹森的說法「已被證明是正確的」<ref>{{Cite web|title=Sen. Scott Jensen says he has 'no regrets' about his COVID-19 comments|url=https://www.startribune.com/sen-scott-jensen-says-complaints-about-covid-19-comments-may-be-political/571650782/|accessdate=2021-01-23|date=2020-07-07|publisher=Star Tribune|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201201344/https://www.startribune.com/sen-scott-jensen-says-complaints-about-covid-19-comments-may-be-political/571650782/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。7月底，明尼蘇達州醫療實踐委員會結束調查，駁回了針對詹森的投訴<ref>{{Cite web|title=Sen. Scott Jensen says probe ends over his comments questioning COVID-19 deaths|url=https://www.startribune.com/physician-senator-says-probe-ends-over-his-comments-questioning-covid-19-deaths/571936032/|accessdate=2021-01-23|date=2020-07-29|publisher=Star Tribune|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210104175637/https://www.startribune.com/physician-senator-says-probe-ends-over-his-comments-questioning-covid-19-deaths/571936032/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 家庭 ==
